---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Le-Kit's Privacy Policy">
  <main style="max-width: 900px; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 0 1rem;">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p>Last updated: March 31, 2026</p>

    <p>This documentation website does not use cookies and does not collect personal information from visitors.</p>

    <h2 id="what-we-collect">What we collect</h2>
    <p>
      We do not intentionally collect names, email addresses, account data, or other personal identifiers through this
      site.
    </p>

    <h2 id="cookies">Cookies and tracking</h2>
    <p>
      No cookies are set for analytics, marketing, or user profiling. No tracking scripts are intentionally included.
    </p>

    <h2 id="consent">Consent</h2>
    <p>
      Since this site does not use cookies and does not process personal data for tracking purposes, a cookie consent
      banner is not required.
    </p>

    <h2 id="github">GitHub interactions</h2>
    <p>
      If you open issues, discussions, or pull requests on GitHub, your data is handled by GitHub according to GitHub's
      own policies and terms.
    </p>

    <h2 id="changes">Changes to this policy</h2>
    <p>
      This policy may be updated if the site behavior changes in the future. If that happens, this page will be updated
      accordingly.
    </p>

    <h2 id="contact">Contact</h2>
    <p>For privacy-related questions about this project, open an issue in the repository.</p>
  </main>
</Layout>
